---
title: Super Green Halloumi Couscous Bowl with Herby Mayo
description: Bright, fresh, and packed with goodness—this couscous bowl is a flavour powerhouse! Flaky, perfectly cooked halloumi sits atop a bed of fluffy couscous packed full of all your favourite veg, tied together with a dreamy drizzle of dill & parsley mayo. It’s wholesome, satisfying, and just the right amount of fancy!

*We’ve replaced the dill & parsley mayonnaise in this recipe with creamy pesto dressing due to local ingredient availability. It’ll
be just as delicious, just follow your recipe card!

